data.title: Preity Zinta enjoys a sunny day with husband Gene Goodenough in California. See pic
data.meta_description: Preity Zinta took to Instagram to share a cute selfie with husband Gene Goodenough from California, USA. The couple seems to be enjoying summertime.
data.text:
Preity Zinta is having a great time under the sun in California, USA, with husband Gene Goodenough. How do we know? Well, the actress shared a cute photo with him from their day out. The two can be seen all ready for summertime in their sunnies. Preity can also be seen wearing a big hat.

advertisement

PREITY ZINTA AND GENE GOODENOUGH’S DAY OUT IN CALIFORNIA

Preity Zinta, who loves gardening at her home in her spare time in California, decided to have a happy day out with her husband Gene Goodenough. The two look great in the selfie Preity shared with her fans and followers on Instagram. Sharing the photo, the actress wrote, “Sunny California selfie #ting (sic).”

Preity Zinta is quite fond of the summers. Recently, she shared another photo enjoying the California sun. She can be seen donning sunglasses and a perfect summer hat in the photo. She captioned it, "Hello sunshine #Ting (sic).”

PREITY ZINTA IS QUITE PROUD OF HER ORGANIC HOME GARDEN

Earlier this month, Preity Zinta showed off her home garden in a video. She also motivated her fans to try it at their homes and be amazed by ‘ghar ki kheti’. She picked some fresh strawberries and said that she planted the seeds with her mother during the lockdown in 2020. Her hard work clearly paid off.

Preity captioned the video, “I cannot explain how excited I am to see fruits & vegetables grow in our backyard. Mom was with me during the lockdown last year & we planted all sorts of herbs, fruit & veggies. Now, I have strawberries, oranges, peaches, guavavas , tomatoes, green & red peppers, green & red chillies, eggplant, mint, basil & lemon grow around the house. I am so proud of our little organic home garden. Thank you ma for making this possible I am loving every bit of this. Try it at home folks - you will be amazed by your own ghar ki kheti #prganicgarden #gharkikheti #strawberries #ting (sic).”

PREITY ZINTA AND GENE GOODENOUGH’S LIFE TOGETHER

Preity Zinta and Gene Goodenough dated for five years before tying the knot on February 29, 2016. The actress moved to the US after her wedding. Preity’s last film release was Bhaiaji Superhit in 2018, which also starred Sunny Deol.
